&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 117px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Osirisplanet.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;NASA drawing of the extrasolar planet Osiris&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;NASA drawing of the extrasolar planet Osiris&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Osirisplanet.jpg/117px-Osirisplanet.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;117&quot; height=&quot;167&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Osirisplanet.jpg/176px-Osirisplanet.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/4/4b/Osirisplanet.jpg/234px-Osirisplanet.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;1305&quot; data-file-height=&quot;1865&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;NASA drawing of the extrasolar planet Osiris&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1095&quot; title=&quot;1095&quot;&gt;1095&lt;/a&gt; – At the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Council_of_Clermont&quot; title=&quot;Council of Clermont&quot;&gt;Council of Clermont&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Pope_Urban_II&quot; title=&quot;Pope Urban II&quot;&gt;Pope Urban&amp;#160;II&lt;/a&gt; called for the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/First_Crusade&quot; title=&quot;First Crusade&quot;&gt;First Crusade&lt;/a&gt;, declaring &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Religious_war&quot; title=&quot;Religious war&quot;&gt;holy war&lt;/a&gt; against the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Muslims&quot; title=&quot;Muslims&quot;&gt;Muslims&lt;/a&gt; who had occupied the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Holy_Land&quot; title=&quot;Holy Land&quot;&gt;Holy Land&lt;/a&gt; and were attacking the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Byzantine_Empire&quot; title=&quot;Byzantine Empire&quot;&gt;Eastern Roman Empire&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1703&quot; title=&quot;1703&quot;&gt;1703&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Great_storm_of_1703&quot; title=&quot;Great storm of 1703&quot;&gt;great storm of 1703&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, one of the most severe storms to strike southern &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Great_Britain&quot; title=&quot;Great Britain&quot;&gt;Great Britain&lt;/a&gt;, destroyed the first &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Eddystone_Lighthouse&quot; title=&quot;Eddystone Lighthouse&quot;&gt;Eddystone Lighthouse&lt;/a&gt; off &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Plymouth&quot; title=&quot;Plymouth&quot;&gt;Plymouth&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1945&quot; title=&quot;1945&quot;&gt;1945&lt;/a&gt; – A consortium of twenty-two U.S. charities founded &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Care_International&quot; title=&quot;Care International&quot;&gt;CARE&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; with the purpose of delivering food aid to Europe in the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Aftermath_of_World_War_II&quot; title=&quot;Aftermath of World War II&quot;&gt;aftermath of World War&amp;#160;II&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2001&quot; title=&quot;2001&quot;&gt;2001&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hubble_Space_Telescope&quot; title=&quot;Hubble Space Telescope&quot;&gt;Hubble Space Telescope&lt;/a&gt; detected &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Sodium&quot; title=&quot;Sodium&quot;&gt;sodium&lt;/a&gt; in the atmosphere of the extrasolar planet &lt;b&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/HD_209458_b&quot; title=&quot;HD 209458 b&quot;&gt;HD 209458 b&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(artist's impression pictured)&lt;/i&gt;, the first planetary atmosphere &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Exoplanet&quot; title=&quot;Exoplanet&quot;&gt;outside our solar system&lt;/a&gt; to be measured.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Increase_Sumner&quot; title=&quot;Increase Sumner&quot;&gt;Increase Sumner&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1746)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Jean_Albert_Gaudry&quot; title=&quot;Jean Albert Gaudry&quot;&gt;Jean Albert Gaudry&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1908)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Gary_Speed&quot; title=&quot;Gary Speed&quot;&gt;Gary Speed&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;2011)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
