	<entry>
		<id>https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20211128000000/en</id>
		<title>On this day: November 28</title>
		<link rel="alternate" type="text/html" href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Special:FeedItem/onthisday/20211128000000/en"/>
		<updated>2021-11-28T00:00:00Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/November_28&quot; title=&quot;November 28&quot;&gt;November 28&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Bukovina_Day&quot; title=&quot;Bukovina Day&quot;&gt;Bukovina Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in Romania (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1918&quot; title=&quot;1918&quot;&gt;1918&lt;/a&gt;)
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 155px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:Tehran_Conference,_1943.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Stalin, Roosevelt, and Churchill in Tehran&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Stalin, Roosevelt, and Churchill in Tehran&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Tehran_Conference%2C_1943.jpg/155px-Tehran_Conference%2C_1943.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;155&quot; height=&quot;126&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Tehran_Conference%2C_1943.jpg/233px-Tehran_Conference%2C_1943.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/d/d8/Tehran_Conference%2C_1943.jpg/310px-Tehran_Conference%2C_1943.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;700&quot; data-file-height=&quot;569&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Stalin, Roosevelt, and Churchill in Tehran&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/936&quot; title=&quot;936&quot;&gt;936&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Shi_Jingtang&quot; title=&quot;Shi Jingtang&quot;&gt;Shi Jingtang&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; was enthroned as the first emperor of the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Later_Jin_(Five_Dynasties)&quot; title=&quot;Later Jin (Five Dynasties)&quot;&gt;Later Jin&lt;/a&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Emperor_Taizong_of_Liao&quot; title=&quot;Emperor Taizong of Liao&quot;&gt;Emperor Taizong of Liao&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1660&quot; title=&quot;1660&quot;&gt;1660&lt;/a&gt; – At London's &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Gresham_College&quot; title=&quot;Gresham College&quot;&gt;Gresham College&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Robert_Boyle&quot; title=&quot;Robert Boyle&quot;&gt;Robert Boyle&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/John_Wilkins&quot; title=&quot;John Wilkins&quot;&gt;John Wilkins&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Christopher_Wren&quot; title=&quot;Christopher Wren&quot;&gt;Christopher Wren&lt;/a&gt; and other leading scientists founded a &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Learned_society&quot; title=&quot;Learned society&quot;&gt;learned society&lt;/a&gt; now known as the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Royal_Society&quot; title=&quot;Royal Society&quot;&gt;Royal Society&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1943&quot; title=&quot;1943&quot;&gt;1943&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/World_War_II&quot; title=&quot;World War II&quot;&gt;World War&amp;#160;II&lt;/a&gt;: U.S. president &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Franklin_D._Roosevelt&quot; title=&quot;Franklin D. Roosevelt&quot;&gt;Franklin D. Roosevelt&lt;/a&gt;, British prime minister &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Winston_Churchill&quot; title=&quot;Winston Churchill&quot;&gt;Winston Churchill&lt;/a&gt;, and Soviet premier &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Joseph_Stalin&quot; title=&quot;Joseph Stalin&quot;&gt;Joseph Stalin&lt;/a&gt; &lt;i&gt;(all three pictured)&lt;/i&gt; met at the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Tehran_Conference&quot; title=&quot;Tehran Conference&quot;&gt;Tehran Conference&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; to discuss war strategy against the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Axis_powers&quot; title=&quot;Axis powers&quot;&gt;Axis powers&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1987&quot; title=&quot;1987&quot;&gt;1987&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/South_African_Airways_Flight_295&quot; title=&quot;South African Airways Flight 295&quot;&gt;South African Airways Flight&amp;#160;295&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; suffered a catastrophic in-flight fire and crashed into the Indian Ocean east of Mauritius, killing all 159 on board.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Abraham_Brueghel&quot; title=&quot;Abraham Brueghel&quot;&gt;Abraham Brueghel&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (bapt.&amp;#160;1631)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Gregorio_Perfecto&quot; title=&quot;Gregorio Perfecto&quot;&gt;Gregorio Perfecto&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1891)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/%CA%BBAbdu%27l-Bah%C3%A1&quot; title=&quot;ʻAbdu&amp;#39;l-Bahá&quot;&gt;ʻAbdu'l-Bahá&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1921)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/November_27&quot; title=&quot;November 27&quot;&gt;November 27&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/November_28&quot; title=&quot;November 28&quot;&gt;November 28&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
