		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/November_29&quot; title=&quot;November 29&quot;&gt;November 29&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;: First day of &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Hanukkah&quot; title=&quot;Hanukkah&quot;&gt;Hanukkah&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; (Judaism, 2021); &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Liberation_Day_(Albania)&quot; title=&quot;Liberation Day (Albania)&quot;&gt;Liberation Day&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in Albania (&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1944&quot; title=&quot;1944&quot;&gt;1944&lt;/a&gt;)
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 172px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:The_Diet.jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;Joint session of the National Diet of Japan in 2002&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;Joint session of the National Diet of Japan in 2002&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/The_Diet.jpg/172px-The_Diet.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;172&quot; height=&quot;114&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/The_Diet.jpg/258px-The_Diet.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/c/c5/The_Diet.jpg/344px-The_Diet.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;400&quot; data-file-height=&quot;266&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;Joint session of the National Diet of Japan in 2002&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/903&quot; title=&quot;903&quot;&gt;903&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Abbasid_Caliphate&quot; title=&quot;Abbasid Caliphate&quot;&gt;Abbasid Caliphate&lt;/a&gt; captured the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Qarmatians&quot; title=&quot;Qarmatians&quot;&gt;Qarmatian&lt;/a&gt; leadership in the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Hama&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Hama&quot;&gt;Battle of Hama&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; in Syria, opening the way for the reconquest of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Tulunids&quot; title=&quot;Tulunids&quot;&gt;Tulunid&lt;/a&gt; Egypt.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1776&quot; title=&quot;1776&quot;&gt;1776&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/American_Revolutionary_War&quot; title=&quot;American Revolutionary War&quot;&gt;American Revolutionary War&lt;/a&gt;: British reinforcements brought an end to the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Patriot_(American_Revolution)&quot; title=&quot;Patriot (American Revolution)&quot;&gt;Patriot&lt;/a&gt; attempt to &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Fort_Cumberland_(1776)&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Fort Cumberland (1776)&quot;&gt;capture&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Fort_Beaus%C3%A9jour&quot; title=&quot;Fort Beauséjour&quot;&gt;Fort Cumberland&lt;/a&gt; in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Nova_Scotia&quot; title=&quot;Nova Scotia&quot;&gt;Nova Scotia&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1890&quot; title=&quot;1890&quot;&gt;1890&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/National_Diet&quot; title=&quot;National Diet&quot;&gt;National Diet&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; of Japan &lt;i&gt;(pictured in session)&lt;/i&gt;, a &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Bicameralism&quot; title=&quot;Bicameralism&quot;&gt;bicameral legislature&lt;/a&gt; modelled after both the German &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Reichstag_(German_Empire)&quot; title=&quot;Reichstag (German Empire)&quot;&gt;Reichstag&lt;/a&gt; and the British &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Westminster_system&quot; title=&quot;Westminster system&quot;&gt;Westminster system&lt;/a&gt;, first met in Tokyo.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2007&quot; title=&quot;2007&quot;&gt;2007&lt;/a&gt; – During their trial for the 2003 &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Oakwood_mutiny&quot; title=&quot;Oakwood mutiny&quot;&gt;Oakwood mutiny&lt;/a&gt;, Philippine soldiers led by Senator &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Antonio_Trillanes&quot; title=&quot;Antonio Trillanes&quot;&gt;Antonio Trillanes&lt;/a&gt; &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Manila_Peninsula_siege&quot; title=&quot;Manila Peninsula siege&quot;&gt;mutinied and seized&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; a conference room in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/The_Peninsula_Manila&quot; title=&quot;The Peninsula Manila&quot;&gt;The Peninsula Manila&lt;/a&gt; hotel in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Makati&quot; title=&quot;Makati&quot;&gt;Makati&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Claudio_Monteverdi&quot; title=&quot;Claudio Monteverdi&quot;&gt;Claudio Monteverdi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1643)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mary_Somerville&quot; title=&quot;Mary Somerville&quot;&gt;Mary Somerville&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1872)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Lalit_Modi&quot; title=&quot;Lalit Modi&quot;&gt;Lalit Modi&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1963)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
