		<updated>2021-12-02T00:00:00Z</updated>

		<summary type="html">&lt;div class=&quot;mw-parser-output&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/December_2&quot; title=&quot;December 2&quot;&gt;December 2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;float:right;margin-left:0.5em;&quot; id=&quot;mp-otd-img&quot;&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;thumbinner mp-thumb&quot; style=&quot;background: transparent; border: none; padding: 0; max-width: 199px;&quot;&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/File:La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_(Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard).jpg&quot; class=&quot;image&quot; title=&quot;The Battle of Austerlitz, 2nd December 1805 by François Gérard&quot;&gt;&lt;img alt=&quot;The Battle of Austerlitz, 2nd December 1805 by François Gérard&quot; src=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_%28Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard%29.jpg/199px-La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_%28Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard%29.jpg&quot; decoding=&quot;async&quot; width=&quot;199&quot; height=&quot;99&quot; srcset=&quot;//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_%28Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard%29.jpg/299px-La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_%28Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard%29.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/ba/La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_%28Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard%29.jpg/398px-La_bataille_d%27Austerlitz._2_decembre_1805_%28Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard%29.jpg 2x&quot; data-file-width=&quot;4000&quot; data-file-height=&quot;1983&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;thumbcaption&quot; style=&quot;padding: 0.25em 0; word-wrap: break-word;&quot;&gt;&lt;i&gt;The Battle of Austerlitz, 2nd December 1805&lt;/i&gt; by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Fran%C3%A7ois_G%C3%A9rard&quot; title=&quot;François Gérard&quot;&gt;François Gérard&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1805&quot; title=&quot;1805&quot;&gt;1805&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/War_of_the_Third_Coalition&quot; title=&quot;War of the Third Coalition&quot;&gt;War of the Third Coalition&lt;/a&gt;: French forces led by &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Napoleon&quot; title=&quot;Napoleon&quot;&gt;Napoleon&lt;/a&gt; decisively defeated a Russo-Austrian army commanded by Tsar &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Alexander_I_of_Russia&quot; title=&quot;Alexander I of Russia&quot;&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;Alexander I&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt; in the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Battle_of_Austerlitz&quot; title=&quot;Battle of Austerlitz&quot;&gt;Battle of Austerlitz&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; &lt;i&gt;(depicted)&lt;/i&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1823&quot; title=&quot;1823&quot;&gt;1823&lt;/a&gt; – U.S. president &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/James_Monroe&quot; title=&quot;James Monroe&quot;&gt;James Monroe&lt;/a&gt; issued the &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Monroe_Doctrine&quot; title=&quot;Monroe Doctrine&quot;&gt;Monroe Doctrine&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, a proclamation of opposition to European colonialism in the &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/New_World&quot; title=&quot;New World&quot;&gt;New World&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1943&quot; title=&quot;1943&quot;&gt;1943&lt;/a&gt; – &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/World_War_II&quot; title=&quot;World War II&quot;&gt;World War II&lt;/a&gt;: The &lt;i&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Luftwaffe&quot; title=&quot;Luftwaffe&quot;&gt;Luftwaffe&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/i&gt; conducted &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Air_raid_on_Bari&quot; title=&quot;Air raid on Bari&quot;&gt;a surprise air raid&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt; on &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Allies_of_World_War_II&quot; title=&quot;Allies of World War II&quot;&gt;Allied&lt;/a&gt; ships in &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Bari&quot; title=&quot;Bari&quot;&gt;Bari&lt;/a&gt;, Italy, sinking twenty-eight ships and releasing one ship's secret cargo of &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Mustard_gas&quot; title=&quot;Mustard gas&quot;&gt;mustard gas&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/1989&quot; title=&quot;1989&quot;&gt;1989&lt;/a&gt; – The &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Malayan_Communist_Party&quot; title=&quot;Malayan Communist Party&quot;&gt;Malayan Communist Party&lt;/a&gt; and the Malaysian government signed &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Peace_Agreement_of_Hat_Yai_(1989)&quot; title=&quot;Peace Agreement of Hat Yai (1989)&quot;&gt;a peace accord&lt;/a&gt; to end &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Communist_insurgency_in_Malaysia_(1968%E2%80%931989)&quot; title=&quot;Communist insurgency in Malaysia (1968–1989)&quot;&gt;the 21-year Communist insurgency&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/2001&quot; title=&quot;2001&quot;&gt;2001&lt;/a&gt; – Less than two months after &lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Enron_scandal&quot; title=&quot;Enron scandal&quot;&gt;disclosing accounting violations&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;, Texas-based energy firm &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Enron&quot; title=&quot;Enron&quot;&gt;Enron&lt;/a&gt; filed for &lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Chapter_11,_Title_11,_United_States_Code&quot; title=&quot;Chapter 11, Title 11, United States Code&quot;&gt;Chapter 11 bankruptcy&lt;/a&gt;, evaporating nearly &lt;span class=&quot;nowrap&quot;&gt;$11 billion&lt;/span&gt; in shareholder wealth.&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated&quot; style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Vincent_Bourne&quot; title=&quot;Vincent Bourne&quot;&gt;Vincent Bourne&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;died&quot;&gt;d.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1747)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Ivan_Bagramyan&quot; title=&quot;Ivan Bagramyan&quot;&gt;Ivan Bagramyan&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1897)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;/wiki/Britney_Spears&quot; title=&quot;Britney Spears&quot;&gt;Britney Spears&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/b&gt;  (&lt;abbr title=&quot;born&quot;&gt;b.&lt;/abbr&gt;&amp;#160;1981)&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;margin-top: 0.5em;&quot;&gt;
More anniversaries: &lt;div class=&quot;hlist hlist-separated inline nowraplinks&quot;&gt;
